race.description: Sportsbet Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tricky maiden with quite a few first starters. FOREVER A DIAMOND (9) brings the race experience and is working towards the winner's stall, having been placed at her last two starts. She's drawn low and maps to get a cosy run. If the gaps come when she needs them, she can sprint over the top of them and win. HARMONIC DANCER (4) has been beaten as favourite in both of her career starts but there has been merit in her performances. She's drawn awkwardly but she's versatile so Opperman can roll forward or take a sit. She can win. BOLD STARLET (8) has shown glimpses of ability and is better than what we saw last start. Expect her to improve. OAK PARK MADDISON (15) is a likely improver that can run in the money, while JOHNNY THE JET (5) is one at a big price that could sneak into the placings.
